{"tid":1418924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求禁止P牌正負評功能","createTime":"2019-08-05T21:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:33:07.000Z","uid":57767,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2257d576ce657b2f82f505fa8f1aefe883e34fd4","tid":1418924,"uid":57767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:44:16.000Z","msg":"第一次開POST，平時做CD ROM正評下就算，但頭先見到個POST屌前線真係好離譜，啲正評增加速度快到一個點，我都未見過有咩高質POST個正評係可以多得咁快，極度懷疑係大量殭屍AC同三毛造成。為免被呢啲AC帶風向都誤導，我強烈要求禁止P牌嘅正負評功能，<span style=\"color: red;\">P牌開POST可以知道佢地係P牌，但正負評係無人知，一係P牌嘅正負評係分開顯示同計算</span>。多謝！<br />\n<br />\n前線勇武義士, 我覺得你地要誠實面對一樣野, 你地係咪開始迷失同享受權力?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417502</a>"},{"pid":"0fa91e2bb828a7d0eeacfc61adfd0a044d361052","tid":1418924,"uid":209050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:47:08.000Z","msg":"[突發］話勇武＂戀權＂嘅人，請入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418897</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"284314dad9090357d2669f1b86fd53a0addaf7a4","tid":1418924,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:31:14.000Z","msg":"所有正負皮都應該取消"},{"pid":"0ac5c0dd34cd7fcbc19b06929c80e1d7f3c848ea","tid":1418924,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:38:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21976b20600c7ad55997551c7e3125f09cfccfc5","tid":1418924,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:39:49.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"7ecc8013d633e0d0fa9814956bf335d72a1a6ba9","tid":1418924,"uid":122604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:43:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e71d269c07fbada1f4a2494ddfe6f38bc8a061fd","tid":1418924,"uid":103262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:42:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38e39dd7da3480a975630ad66c427905317ded00","tid":1418924,"uid":10326